[["Map",1,2,9,10,77,78],"meta::meta",["Map",3,4,5,6,7,8],"astro-version","5.18.2","content-config-digest","6832515f928624f6","astro-config-digest","{\"root\":{},\"srcDir\":{},\"publicDir\":{},\"outDir\":{},\"cacheDir\":{},\"site\":\"https://example.com\",\"compressHTML\":true,\"base\":\"/\",\"trailingSlash\":\"ignore\",\"output\":\"static\",\"scopedStyleStrategy\":\"attribute\",\"build\":{\"format\":\"directory\",\"client\":{},\"server\":{},\"assets\":\"_astro\",\"serverEntry\":\"entry.mjs\",\"redirects\":true,\"inlineStylesheets\":\"auto\",\"concurrency\":1},\"server\":{\"open\":false,\"host\":false,\"port\":4321,\"streaming\":true,\"allowedHosts\":[]},\"redirects\":{},\"image\":{\"endpoint\":{\"route\":\"/_image\"},\"service\":{\"entrypoint\":\"astro/assets/services/sharp\",\"config\":{}},\"domains\":[],\"remotePatterns\":[],\"responsiveStyles\":false},\"devToolbar\":{\"enabled\":true},\"markdown\":{\"syntaxHighlight\":{\"type\":\"shiki\",\"excludeLangs\":[\"math\"]},\"shikiConfig\":{\"langs\":[],\"langAlias\":{},\"theme\":\"github-dark\",\"themes\":{},\"wrap\":false,\"transformers\":[]},\"remarkPlugins\":[],\"rehypePlugins\":[],\"remarkRehype\":{},\"gfm\":true,\"smartypants\":true},\"security\":{\"checkOrigin\":true,\"allowedDomains\":[],\"actionBodySizeLimit\":1048576},\"env\":{\"schema\":{},\"validateSecrets\":false},\"experimental\":{\"clientPrerender\":false,\"contentIntellisense\":false,\"headingIdCompat\":false,\"preserveScriptOrder\":false,\"liveContentCollections\":false,\"csp\":false,\"staticImportMetaEnv\":false,\"chromeDevtoolsWorkspace\":false,\"failOnPrerenderConflict\":false,\"svgo\":false},\"legacy\":{\"collections\":false}}","books",["Map",11,12,20,21,29,30,37,38,45,46,53,54,61,62,69,70],"placeholder-book-1",{"id":11,"data":13,"filePath":18,"digest":19},{"title":14,"kind":15,"year":16,"description":17},"La corte de las diablas","Book","2026","La Corte de las Diablas se gestó en mí como un alarido que nació del vientre. Soy producto de una machista con actitudes asumidas como normales hasta que mi cuerpo comenzó a gritar, y entonces decidí escribir para liberarlo.  A través de mis Diablas existo porque el tiempo que tengo es limitado y he de aprovecharlo al máximo, con una sola vida no me alcanza, es por eso las necesito también a ellas. No soy sola una voz, somos muchas. Y la voz no es solo mía, también es tuya. LEÉLO, Y CONVERSEMOS","src/content/books/placeholder-book-1.json","1861887bba475aea","placeholder-story-1",{"id":20,"data":22,"filePath":27,"digest":28},{"title":23,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":25,"url":26},"Sinestesia","Short Story","Mujer en paños menores se arroja por el balcón.","https://marmioni.substack.com/p/sinestesia","src/content/books/placeholder-story-1.json","15e864840a24bfbf","placeholder-story-3",{"id":29,"data":31,"filePath":35,"digest":36},{"title":32,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":33,"url":34},"Ex Convicta","Pieza ganadora del segundo premio del Concurso del Escritor de Substack, con el tema “pequeños placeres”","https://open.substack.com/pub/marmioni/p/ex-convicta?r=5lxmvs&utm_campaign=post&utm_medium=web","src/content/books/placeholder-story-3.json","b1a2849a3d6227a5","placeholder-story-4",{"id":37,"data":39,"filePath":43,"digest":44},{"title":40,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":41,"url":42},"Estúpida","El nuevo paciente aparece en la puerta con su sonrisa de comercial, se instala en el diván con el exceso de confianza de quien ha hecho esto muchas veces antes.","https://open.substack.com/pub/marmioni/p/estupida?r=5lxmvs&utm_campaign=post&utm_medium=web","src/content/books/placeholder-story-4.json","ab0db9a28a34c9ca","placeholder-story-2",{"id":45,"data":47,"filePath":51,"digest":52},{"title":48,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":49,"url":50},"Yo maté a Dios","Me quité la vida una noche de verano y fue así como accedí inexplicablemente al cielo","https://open.substack.com/pub/marmioni/p/yo-mate-a-dios?r=5lxmvs&utm_campaign=post&utm_medium=web","src/content/books/placeholder-story-2.json","1ce51fb6bc86f028","placeholder-story-6",{"id":53,"data":55,"filePath":59,"digest":60},{"title":56,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":57,"url":58},"Final Feliz","Me dijeron que todas mis historias terminan con finales trágicos, así que hoy vengo dispuesta a entregarles un final feliz.","https://open.substack.com/pub/marmioni/p/final-feliz?r=5lxmvs&utm_campaign=post&utm_medium=web","src/content/books/placeholder-story-6.json","4caae618043df223","placeholder-story-5",{"id":61,"data":63,"filePath":67,"digest":68},{"title":64,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":65,"url":66},"Virgen","-Me llamo Virgen y soy adicta al sexo.","https://open.substack.com/pub/marmioni/p/virgen?r=5lxmvs&utm_campaign=post&utm_medium=web","src/content/books/placeholder-story-5.json","f16c83785bcfc033","placeholder-story-7",{"id":69,"data":71,"filePath":75,"digest":76},{"title":72,"kind":24,"year":16,"description":73,"url":74},"Mi Crush","Pero yo aceleré porque venía medio peda y me fui directo a la zanja. Entonces llegó el rescate en forma de una mano que abrió la puerta y luego me tomó en sus brazos. En ese momento me enamoré","https://open.substack.com/pub/marmioni/p/mi-crush?r=5lxmvs&utm_campaign=post-expanded-share&utm_medium=web","src/content/books/placeholder-story-7.json","bec451cd26ac4625","media",["Map",79,80],"interview-01",{"id":79,"data":81,"filePath":86,"digest":87},{"title":82,"outlet":83,"url":84,"image":85},"Proscrita: Mar Mioni","Relatos Neuróticos","https://open.substack.com/pub/relatosneuroticos/p/proscrita-mar-mioni?utm_source=share&utm_medium=android&r=5lxmvs","/images/entrevista.jpeg","src/content/media/interview-01.json","31adb279d1a5a139"]